
Ranger Help for: plains
=======================

SUMMARY:    
The plains are just as they sound, large flat grassland expanses. Some
plains are mere large fields though. They are charaterized by temperate
climates and some life. The population of Rangers is quite a bit
smaller in the plains than in other wooded areas. Plains can be found
on Darkwind and some arctic plains can be found in Hyperborea.

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

